{"word":"G572 - ἁπλότης - haplótēs - hap-lot'-ace - Bountifulness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἁπλότης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>haplótēs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hap-lot'-ace"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bountifulness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வஞ்சனையில்லாமை, கபடமின்மை, உதாரத்துவம், உதாரகுணம், உண்மை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"singleness, simplicity, sincerity, mental honesty"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G573 - ἁπλοῦς - haploûs - hap-looce'/573\">G573</a>; <i>singleness</i>, that is, (subjectively) <i>sincerity</i> (<i>without dissimulation</i> or <i>self seeking</i>), or (objectively) <i>generosity</i> (<i>copious bestowal</i>): - bountifulness, liberal (-ity), simplicity, singleness."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G572 - ἁπλότης - haplótēs - hap-lot'-ace/572\">G572</a>, <a href=\"#/G573 - ἁπλοῦς - haploûs - hap-looce'/573\">G573</a>"}]}